      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so empty lately. like, no matter what i do, it doesn't actually matter. we're just biological accidents on a rock spinning through a void that doesn't care if we exist or not. there's no higher purpose, no grand design, just infinite nothingness. it's hard to find a reason to keep pushing through the day when the math just doesn't add up to anything.",
