      "content": "yeah exactly. it's just so heavy. like people try to offer these little band-aids of \"hope\" or \"meaning,\" but it all feels so fake and superficial. if there really is nothing out there, and we're just drifting until we eventually stop, then why does it have to be such a constant, exhausting struggle to just stay here?",
